data.description: Beautiful Updated Home In Pecan Valley on corner lot with circular driveway. 5  bedrooms, 2 living areas, formal dining, 2 story high entry. Beautiful hardwood floors in dining & formal living, den. Tile floors in entry, hallways, kitchen & baths, new carpet in all bedrooms. Large secluded master suite, updated master bath, granite countertops, double uindermount sink, subway tiled shower, whirlpool tub, tiled floors, large walk-in closet. Awesome kitchen, beautiful granite countertops, plenty of cabinets, beautiful tile backsplashes, pantry, cabinets, new stainless steel appliances. 1/2 bath, vanity, modern gray & white colors. Big storage under stairs. Den with wood burning fireplace, updated fireplace surroundlngs, wood floors, 2 story high ceilings, 4 bedrooms upstairs-one is large can be game room. Large dinette area, double French doors to yard, wood fence, storage shed.
